            <fr:title text="n-truncated types are closed under retracts"><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> types are closed under <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" title="Retract" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025" type="local">retracts</fr:link></fr:title>
