          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Any <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" title="Retract" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025" type="local">retract</fr:link> of an <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> type is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>2</fr:month><fr:day>17</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>By induction on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>; the base cases for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-1]]></fr:tex> are given by <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002V/" title="The identity map is n-truncated for all n" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002V/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002V" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002V/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-002V" /></fr:link> and <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" title="propositions are closed under retracts" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0026" /></fr:link> respectively. In the inductive step, we assume that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> exhibits <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> as a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" title="Retract" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025" type="local">retract</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and that for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y:A]]></fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x=_Ay]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n+1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> to show that for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u,v:B]]></fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u=_Bv]]></fr:tex> is likewise <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" title="n-truncated type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n+1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>. The result follows from our assumption and the fact that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u=_Bv]]></fr:tex> is (by <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-003U/" title="Lifting retracts to identifications" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-003U/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-003U" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-003U/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-003U" /></fr:link>) a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" title="Retract" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0025" type="local">retract</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[su=_Asv]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
